Package: scAmbi
Type: Package
Title: Mapping Ambiguity Overdispersion Correction for scRNA-seq
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Sean T.", "Bresnahan", email = "stbresnahan@mdanderson.org", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Tools to estimate and correct overdispersion from read-to-transcript mapping ambiguity
    for single-cell RNA-seq quantifications (e.g., Salmon Alevin bootstraps), and utilities to
    compare biological coefficient of variation (BCV) before/after correction.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/sbresnahan/scAmbi
BugReports: https://github.com/sbresnahan/scAmbi/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.2)
